# Monorepo root .gitignore.
# Each subproject (api-usa, tigress-picks-prototype) also has its own
# .gitignore. This file is a belt-and-braces guard so secrets, builds, and
# OS noise can never accidentally land in a commit run from the repo root.

# Dependencies
**/node_modules/

# Build output
**/dist/
**/build/
**/dist-ssr/
**/.tsbuildinfo
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# Environment files — secrets. .env.example is the only checked-in template.
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# Editor / OS noise
.vscode/
.idea/
.history/
.DS_Store
*.log

# Vercel local state
.vercel/

# Personal scratch files / external upstreams that shouldn't ship.
# worldcup2026-iran/ is the rezarahiminia/worldcup2026 upstream — used as a
# reference for real WC2026 fixture data, not our code.
abandoned/
worldcup-picks/
worldcup2026-iran/
